        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas burner won&rsquo;t ignite <span class="gas-badge">MOST COMMON</span></div><div class="repair-desc">One or more surface burners won&rsquo;t light, clicking continuously</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$160&ndash;$320</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ igniter or electrode if needed</div></td>
            <td>Spark igniter replacement, spark electrode, spark module. Boilover moisture often resolves with drying &mdash; no part needed. We check all burners while on site.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas burner flame uneven / won&rsquo;t stay lit <span class="gas-badge">GAS</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Flame too low, flickering, or goes out immediately</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$175&ndash;$360</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ valve or cap if needed</div></td>
            <td>Burner cap misalignment (often free), gas valve adjustment, burner orifice cleaning, thermocouple (standing pilot models)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Electric surface element not heating</div><div class="repair-desc">One or more burners dead on electric range</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$160&ndash;$320</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ element or switch</div></td>
            <td>Surface heating element replacement, infinite switch (controls heat level). We test all elements while on site.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Infinite switch failure</div><div class="repair-desc">Burner won&rsquo;t turn off, uncontrolled heat, or won&rsquo;t turn on</div></td>
